#: manual.docbook:6821
msgid "Attack"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: glossdef/para
#: manual.docbook:6823
msgid "This is the first phase of an <link linkend=\"def.adsr\">ADSR</link> envelope. It represents the amount of <emphasis>time</emphasis> to increase the volume of a note from 0 (triggering) to full <link linkend=\"def.velocity\">velocity</link>."
